data.description: Beautiful brick home in the heart of Evans. Great Columbia County Schools. Kitchen features stained cabinets, granite countertops, recessed lighting, stainless steel appliances including Refrigerator, dishwasher, glass cooktop range & built in microwave. Walk In Pantry, Home/office work station. Hardwood floors in foyer, kitchen & breakfast area & dry bar. New carpet being installed in family room & Owners Suite. Family room has  fireplace & is open to kitchen area. Back yard is fenced with covered patio. Downstairs Owners suite has trey ceiling, bath has separate tub and shower, double vanities & walk in custom closet. Upstairs 2nd bedroom has its own bath, 3rd & 4th bedrooms share a Jack & Jill bath. Loft area has closet and large enough to be a bedroom, great for gaming or home office. This home located conveniently to Ft. Gordon, Recreation, schools and shopping. Neighborhood amenities include 2 pools, pavilion, walking trails, sidewalks & shady park.
